    <h1 style=center>What is this system?</h1>
    <br>
    The Landlord Data Tracking System (LDTS) is a web-based application that landlords can use to store data about properties that they own.
    <br />
    <br />
    <br />
    
    <h1>What details does the system store about the properties?</h1>
    At the moment, the LDTS can store informatino such as the following:
    <br />
     - House Number
     <br />
     - Street Name
     <br />
     - City
     <br />
     - Country
     <br />
     The dates of when you accquired particular certificates can be stored in this system too.
     Certificates such as the following:
     <br />
     - CP12
     <br />
     - PATS
     <br />
     - EICR
     <br />
     - EPC
